('9407e2c4-9a43-5218-a691-23ff24c00e4d', 2, 'rpls_license_skilled_trade_moat', 'positive', NULL, 'TX RPLS license = 4yr ABET-accredited surveying or equivalent + 4yr supervised survey-in-training + Tex. Occ. Code Ch. 1071 state exam. ~3,700 active RPLS statewide (TBPELS roster May 2026). Workforce documented as aging (TSPS workforce-shortage reports cite avg RPLS age >55).', 'tbpels_rpls_roster_aggregate', 'https://pels.texas.gov/roster/ls_rosters.html', '2026-05-16'),
